{"id": "1523012079261585468", "channel_id": "1523003072035553441", "author_id": "400656449417773066", "author_name": "cpu7954", "content": "助戰推薦優先借取 這邊安利個薩摩佬的茉夏\n另外助戰一般需要對方回關才能使用\n但有10個常用助戰的名額不需要對方回關就可以用", "timestamp": "2026-07-04T17:06:15.892000+00:00", "thread_id": "1523003072035553441", "attachments": [{"id": "1523012078791692380", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2660920, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1523003072035553441/1523012078791692380/image.png?ex=6a4a8f07&is=6a493d87&hm=51ef41aa91f8842794074215c5e1bd9e581303f60cbfb9df14fe7521ec2e23bd&"}]}
